Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.40,0:00:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好，卡萊多之星要開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.30,0:00:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀看卡萊多之星的時候要注意保持屋內亮度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.10,0:00:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要離電視太近了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.40,0:00:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那麼，那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.70,0:00:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家來到陌生的地方\N會有非常不安的感覺嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是新鮮事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.00,0:00:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有以前學會的\N記住的那些本領是不夠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.70,0:00:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次總是不斷的有事情發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.30,0:00:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢？呢？呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.60,0:02:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始可以休息啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.80,0:02:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一個星期的時間可以好好休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.00,0:02:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾真想出去旅行一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.90,0:02:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空真是精神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.90,0:02:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可要好好休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.00,0:02:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.90,0:02:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.10,0:02:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好想去那些沒有去過的小鎮玩玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.20,0:02:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.50,0:02:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什……什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.10,0:02:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個不是飛機票嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.50,0:02:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這是獎勵我\N一直以來的努力的禮物嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.80,0:02:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,——太好了\N——你可以如願以償了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.60,0:03:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之還是如願以償的可以出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去我以前的一位好友\N派克先生的劇團參加友情演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.80,0:03:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是工作啊？哈哈哈哈哈（-_-！慘笑）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.20,0:03:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死靈--犧牲的卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不吉利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.30,0:03:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了那邊我就是你的經理人了\N先有個心理準備吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.90,0:03:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.70,0:03:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過能和健一起來真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.70,0:03:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人生！偶爾也有讓人驚喜的事啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.40,0:03:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們要去的是西雅圖巡迴馬戲團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.00,0:03:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西雅圖巡迴馬戲團？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.30,0:04:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是移動雜技團\N表演的節目有吹火把，耍飛刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也有魔術雜耍表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.30,0:04:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要吹火把麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.50,0:04:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.90,0:04:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陌生人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.10,0:04:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.50,0:04:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這邊沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.60,0:04:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭候多時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.40,0:04:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空•苗木野小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.10,0:04:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到西雅圖巡迴馬戲團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有吹火把啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.20,0:05:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.60,0:05:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了，連觀眾都上臺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.80,0:05:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.00,0:05:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別再胡鬧了，塔克\N魔術雜耍結束以後就快點下場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是孩子們喜歡……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.50,0:05:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要找藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.00,0:05:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.90,0:05:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了很多次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有偷吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.40,0:05:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你偷吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.80,0:06:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹我們的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.80,0:06:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位是空•苗木野小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.40,0:06:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是從卡萊多劇團來的，請多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是空的經理人健•洛賓斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.50,0:06:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚吃特別大餐燒牛肉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有肉吃！有肉吃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.50,0:06:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天的劇目有客人\N在就演那個難得演的劇目吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空•苗木野小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.60,0:06:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你出演主角的公主角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主角？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.20,0:06:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是公主嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道我行不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，肯定不行的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.10,0:06:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行-不行-不行-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.00,0:06:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我會努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行-不行-不行-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劇情非常的簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.30,0:07:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你扮演的是被魔女抓去妹妹的公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.40,0:07:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美拉和美洛又把胡蘿蔔扔了哦\N羅米莉姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.80,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次再扔了就沒飯給你們吃了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔女的角色由帕米拉出演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.20,0:07:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出演怪力男的塔克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.60,0:07:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.00,0:07:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著和飛刀怪人戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後直奔魔女的老巢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.60,0:07:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派克，不要忘了介紹我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.20,0:07:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不會忘了你的，他叫迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是你唯一的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.00,0:07:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們二人必須齊心協力救出那對雙胞胎\N最後成為戀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結局是HAPPY END
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.10,0:07:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 也請你多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.40,0:08:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛！\N我覺得根本不必成為戀人什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.30,0:08:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我喂下孩子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在看劇本呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.30,0:08:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個劇本只寫了臺詞\N卻沒有寫表演內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.00,0:08:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼演好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.20,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了\N只要明天彩排的時候聽一下解說就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先好好睡一覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.70,0:08:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡不著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.90,0:08:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星星真漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.20,0:08:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.80,0:08:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.50,0:08:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你一直以來的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然說這話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.10,0:09:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為在我困惑的時候\N總是你在幫助我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.00,0:09:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總應該謝謝你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.10,0:09:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你的話，《人魚公主》\N還有和蕾拉小姐的競演我一定都演不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.00,0:09:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼說，都是你自己努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.10,0:09:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.70,0:09:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，空很努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.50,0:09:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是太努力了，好像努力到了\N有點我可望而不可及的程度了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚還是好好休息下比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是太吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.60,0:09:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我會努力睡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.40,0:09:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，努力睡覺精神好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.90,0:09:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個寶寶哭了一整晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.00,0:09:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，塔克的鼾聲也不相上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.40,0:10:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男演員也都不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼彩排呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.60,0:10:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是不彩排了咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不彩排了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.90,0:10:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，幾乎從來不彩排的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.00,0:10:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家現在都在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.60,0:10:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢？\N到晚上的表演前都是自由活動時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.90,0:10:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是舞臺方向傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.80,0:10:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人都找不到\N我正不知道如何是好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家可能都出去玩了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.50,0:10:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到小鎮上人們的熱情款待\N所以才都去吃喝玩耍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.50,0:10:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下，真的不彩排了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不彩排的話我沒法演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.80,0:10:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.60,0:10:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我給你個重要的提示吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.40,0:10:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.30,0:11:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天看了我們的表演就應該有點明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.10,0:11:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的成員每個人都有自己的特長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.50,0:11:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,故事情節是配合每個人的特長臨時發揮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.40,0:11:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以經常是根據觀眾的反應延續故事的情節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.30,0:11:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據觀眾的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.10,0:11:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N能夠表演出什麼樣的故事就看你的本領了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先走一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.30,0:11:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的本領？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.30,0:11:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要救你妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.00,0:11:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我活著隨時都可以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.60,0:12:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……可以出場了嗎？可以了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.50,0:12:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.80,0:12:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點……出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.50,0:12:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是公主啊，得擺個漂亮的造型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.40,0:12:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞，美洛，你們在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說被魔女……啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.60,0:12:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等下 什麼 怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.40,0:12:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都很順利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順利？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.10,0:13:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 慢點 那個 糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.40,0:13:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.80,0:13:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在讓我來試試公主的勇氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裏，公主殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去無法收場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.60,0:13:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拙劣的演技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.10,0:14:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的人都是什麼態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.50,0:14:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果還是這樣對待我們\N明天的表演就拒絕出演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.10,0:14:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果空•苗木野小姐也這麼說的話\N我也無可奈何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.30,0:14:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來他們似乎很喜歡欺負新人\N今天表演時都擺明瞭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.80,0:14:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想回去的話\N我會去和卡洛斯解釋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.40,0:14:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是嘲笑我的失敗，那沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.80,0:14:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是事實並非如此\N大家是嘲笑我一個陌生人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.30,0:15:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的表演觀眾和演員共同參與\N氣氛融洽，演出非常成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.40,0:15:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，今天從頭到底都是把我當一個外來人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不讓我有表演的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.60,0:15:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在說帕米拉嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.20,0:15:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕米拉做的確過分了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.60,0:15:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你在橫杆上的時候\N有沒有仔細觀察過帕米拉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.40,0:15:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你浪費了帕米拉最精彩的一幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.40,0:15:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.90,0:15:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點睡覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.20,0:15:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先前的事，對不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.80,0:15:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你是不想回去了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.10,0:16:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏和卡萊多不同，不是只按照劇本的\N安排表演就能獲得掌聲那麼簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.30,0:16:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多的表演並不簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還不回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.20,0:16:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在這裏\N以這裏的劇團團員的身份表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.80,0:16:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以明天的表演請一定讓我參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.40,0:16:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是心血來潮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚者的正位啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正象我擔心的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.10,0:16:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你是遇到難題意志消沉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是擔心我才來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.90,0:16:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，躲在狹小的手提箱裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.40,0:16:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你這麼意志消沉，看來我真是來對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.70,0:16:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，夫魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.80,0:16:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈！真是來對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.40,0:16:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是……是只蟑螂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.40,0:17:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先還是從瞭解舞臺結構開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.20,0:17:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個舞臺非常的狹窄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.00,0:17:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一部分和觀眾的距離非常近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.00,0:17:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說實話，卡萊多的舞臺上觀眾\N是看不出演員的微妙的表情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.80,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過在這裏你的任何\N微妙表情都能被看的一清二楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.10,0:17:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多的演技在這裏不適用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.30,0:17:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏必須根據所有的\N演員和觀眾的反應來表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.10,0:17:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能夠做到這點\N則不可能成為這個團體的一員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主啊！如果想要救你妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.70,0:17:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我活著隨時都可以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.30,0:17:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.50,0:17:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.50,0:17:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.60,0:18:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞，美洛，你們在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.40,0:18:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說……被魔女……抓走了嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.70,0:18:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會……救出……你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.10,0:18:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？怎麼沒有動靜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.40,0:18:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.60,0:18:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧-來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.10,0:18:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，在這裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝！謝謝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐太棒了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.50,0:18:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.60,0:18:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我正中目標吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.20,0:19:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.00,0:19:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裏，公主殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.40,0:19:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看看主角應有的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.40,0:19:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正上方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.90,0:19:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.60,0:20:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很棒啊，帕米拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.50,0:20:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次看到這樣的表演呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.50,0:20:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這個絕招不是\N試一次二次就能成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.10,0:20:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我不想輸給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.00,0:20:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.00,0:20:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏不需要什麼花哨的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.30,0:20:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏需要擁有的是\N每天都能延續劇情的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.20,0:20:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多的舞臺並不代表所有的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.70,0:20:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個舞臺都有最合適它自己的表演\N我已經都明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.70,0:20:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也在卡萊多劇團呆過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.10,0:20:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不合適那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能按照自己的喜好去表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.50,0:20:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.40,0:20:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你很合適嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.20,0:20:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還從來沒這麼想過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.10,0:21:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在卡萊多劇團一定很需要你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過很遺憾，合作只能到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.60,0:21:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天表演的時候，美洛的腳受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.80,0:21:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然比預定的早了些時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.50,0:21:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這次的公演也只能到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.90,0:21:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.00,0:21:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是橄欖枝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.30,0:21:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每到一處表演時，都會這麼種上幾株
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.20,0:21:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派克的嗜好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.40,0:21:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,象徵著和平的橄欖枝即使再怎麼澆水\N也會在下個季節再度沉睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.60,0:21:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的表演也正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.40,0:21:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過再怎麼說也不能\N拿它來做美味的沙拉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.00,0:21:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的確具有不同凡響的魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.00,0:21:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕米拉和其他很多人\N都演過那個公主的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.00,0:21:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而她的表演讓人覺得\N有種不可思議的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.50,0:22:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有人去培養它\N才能之花是不可能開放的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.20,0:22:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.80,0:22:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好培養空的才能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.00,0:22:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕米拉\N一定要來卡萊多看看我們的表演哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.30,0:22:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我高興了再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.80,0:22:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.60,0:22:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告：卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.50,0:22:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來這裏已經不需要我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.10,0:22:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.30,0:22:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？莎莉小姐也會意志消沉？而且是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.90,0:22:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,持續了十年之久的三角戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.90,0:22:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然好像是我不能理解的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.80,0:22:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣下去可不行啊！啊！啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.60,0:22:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.00,0:22:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀是夢想，飛向空
